snippet: Cardiff City manager Ole Gunnar Solskjaer believes their surprise 1-0 Premier League win at Southampton on Saturday can galvanise his relegation-threatened side after a difficult week for the club....

headline.print_headline: Cardiff End Difficult Week on a High With Saints Win
headline.main: Cardiff End Difficult Week on a High With Saints Win

lead_paragraph: Cardiff City manager Ole Gunnar Solskjaer believes their surprise 1-0 Premier League win at Southampton on Saturday can galvanise his relegation-threatened side after a difficult week for the club.
